@SAHealth China hide the truth and spread the virus since 2019
Millions of people in the world are killed

@SAHealth Wow Twitter is a sesspool 😂😂😂

Anyone screeching to keep the restrictions is an absolute tossbag 😂😂😂😂
@danny_mans @SAHealth Actually if you look at the list of underlying conditions, it covers a hell of a lot of the population!!

@nomes00 @SAHealth I’m tripled vaxxed and have had the virus twice, it sucks and I was sick for weeks, but I can’t continue to live this on again off again life - and the broad majority of Australians agree with me.

@nomes00 @SAHealth Because the majority don’t have underlying health conditions and the majority have suffered for 2 years, it’s time to move forward, this doesn’t ever go away and we can’t live like this forever. If it’s not alpha it’s delta, or omicron or ba2 - there’s never a “better” time.
@Aussie_Shopper @SAHealth Happy for you to stay home 24/7. Let other people actually make a living.
@alanceojlb @SAHealth We are behind the times once again. ISO rules are ridiculous in SA. This change is for the better
